{"tid":190228,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"常盤貴子到「混浴」溫泉 全裸入池惹阿伯暴動了！","createTime":"2017-04-07T03:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T05:19:45.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa085d01784dee47217d538eabd2fe53de996780","tid":190228,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"日本「純潔玉女」常盤貴子出道以來以清純形象擄獲大票宅男粉絲的心，有「日劇女王」稱號；日前她在節目《徹子的房間》中提到，先前曾到美國俄勒岡州旅遊，聽到當地有溫泉可以泡，隨即興沖沖的前往，不過該處是「混浴」溫泉，也就是男女混合在同一池，她的出現讓在場阿伯一陣躁動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BByIyHH.img?h=373&amp;w=624&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=570&amp;y=403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBByIyHH.img%3Fh%3D373%26w%3D624%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D570%26y%3D403&h=be56527b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲常盤貴子日前穿著典雅和服上《徹子的房間》。<br />\n<br />\n常盤貴子日前在《徹子的房間》中自爆，先前到美國俄勒岡州旅遊，聽聞當地有個溫泉，她興奮地向居民問路，對方看她是女生，馬上警告是「混浴池」，但她在日本其實已經很習慣混浴文化、並不太在意。只是到現場後，才發現在池裡的男性多是有年紀的「阿伯」，難得看到有年輕女生出現，大夥兒紛紛靠近打招呼，她也「順應民意」輪流到不同的角落泡溫泉，「泡的當下是不會尷尬的，且（美國的）溫泉和日本的泡起來很不一樣，是個很有趣的體驗。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBzt36S.img?h=400&amp;w=500&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBzt36S.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D500%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df&h=b9716dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲常盤貴子年過40歲仍保養得宜。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，常盤貴子嫁給男星長塚圭史後就淡出螢光幕，2014年曾受邀出席節目《あさイチ》擔任來賓，年過40歲的她纖瘦身材和白嫩肌膚依舊，完全看不出歲月痕跡，雖然一度被指發福劣化，但許多人認為「40歲保養成這樣已經很厲害了。」"},{"pid":"cda40faad66f4021cc0031c14eaed8e4f3d5ec34","tid":190228,"uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d374206e596ae8567d9ad0626c3c37a4e874f98","tid":190228,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"H漫？"},{"pid":"24efcf1fccf45cd266fc44e2800ae47420f85a54","tid":190228,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c90a1a9bddd7b32925f9ac2ffe54f125ef8bef","tid":190228,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"Adidas和服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59440e01458892a09507eb9a240cbbff1e197d69","tid":190228,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n常盤又無<br />\n千雪又無<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odZjc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodZjc.gif&h=ead55f55&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}